  <title translate="true">MT-POP-MotionDesigner-X-Units</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword translate="true">X-axis:<keyword translate="true">Units</keyword></keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="" style="text-align:left; text-indent:0px; margin-top:0px; margin-right:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; line-height:1.00; background-color:transparent; white-space:normal; page-break-inside:auto; page-break-after:auto; border:none; tabstops:none;"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="1" colcount="1" style="width:450px;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">X–axis units</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> have units based on “</text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">counts,” time, angle, </text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">or</text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true"> cycles</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">.</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Select the </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">X-axis units</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> in the </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small" translate="true">Active-Motion-Settings dialog</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-style:italic;" translate="true">. </text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">The options are: “Counts”, secs (seconds); msecs (milliseconds); </text><text styleclass="Popup Box" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true">cycles </text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">(machine cycles); degrees; radians. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso-small"><text styleclass="SeeAlso-small" translate="true">See </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Edit-Active-Motion-Settings" anchor="Motion" styleclass="SeeAlso-small" translate="true">Active Motion Settings &gt;Motion tab</link></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso-small"><text styleclass="SeeAlso-small" translate="true">See also </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-POP-Counts" styleclass="SeeAlso-small" translate="true">X-axis Counts</link></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
